1. Project Overview

Project Name: MathFuel
Category: Adaptive Learning Intelligence Platform (EdTech)

Mission:
Transform math learning into a personalized, data-driven experience that adapts in real time to each student’s ability, behavior, and confidence level.

Core Idea:
MathFuel is not a “math app.”
It is a learning engine that:

Diagnoses skill gaps
Adapts difficulty dynamically
Tracks confidence + engagement
Surfaces insights to parents, teachers, and admins
